    public class KeyedCEPPatternOperator<IN,KEY>
extends AbstractKeyedCEPPatternOperator<IN,KEY,Map<String,IN>>
    CEP pattern operator which only returns fully matched event patterns stored in a Map. The events are indexed by the event names associated in the pattern specification. The operator works on keyed input data.
